			<item>
				<title>Waline V3 &#43; Supabase Pitfall Guide: Implementing a Serverless Comment System for Hugo</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/2026/6/25/waline-comment-en/</link>
				<pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/2026/6/25/waline-comment-en/</guid>
				<description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This comment system utilizes Waline v3.15.2 as a serverless backend and Supabase (PostgreSQL) for data storage. You can enjoy a completely free comment system without the need to set up or maintain a personal server.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-supabase-database-configuration&#34;&gt;1. Supabase Database Configuration&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://supabase.com/&#34;&gt;Supabase Official Website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;11-create-an-organization&#34;&gt;1.1 Create an Organization&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;For newly registered users, a &amp;ldquo;New organization&amp;rdquo; button will appear. Click it, enter your organization name, choose &amp;ldquo;Personal&amp;rdquo; for the type, select the free plan, and click create. &#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;supabase--create-organization.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
